articles.title: 'AGT' opera singer shocks with Ariana Grande, Stevie Nicks impression - USA TODAY
articles.description: "America's Got Talent" on Tuesday delivered inspirational auditions that tugged at the heartstrings and others straight from the depths of hell.
articles.content:
• 'America's Got Talent' returned Tuesday with more shocking and inspiring auditions.
  • Lily Meola clinched the Golden Buzzer from Heidi Klum after singing her original song "Daydream."

articles.title: America's obsession with freedom is making men fat: study - New York Post
